1138.question: What is new state-of-the-art performance on CoNLL-2009 dataset?
1138.response: {'Answer': 'The new state-of-the-art performance on the CoNLL-2009 dataset is an F1 score of 87.70 as achieved by RELAWE (DEP&RELPATH) for English and 87.35 (for Chinese) by RELAWE (DEP&RELPATH) + BERT.'}
1138.answer: In closed setting 84.22 F1 and in open 87.35 F1.
